{"tid":2381474,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人屬於高敏感一族？","createTime":"2021-01-26T15:02:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-31T05:22:18.000Z","uid":86587,"like":9,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5c4c1ff25746e81a0c10a57cbceb91a2ed927b26","tid":2381474,"uid":86587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T15:02:28.000Z","msg":"唔係毒撚攞嚟打J嘅term，而係真係有呢類人存在<br />\n<br />\n轉自台灣網站<a href=\"https://www.managertoday.com.tw/articles/view/58981\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.managertoday.com.tw%2Farticles%2Fview%2F58981&d=TIKlq4bXcOIiQck3m%2BQSv1EyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=3df9d274\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.managertoday.com.tw/articles/view/58981</a><br />\n高敏感有 8 大特徵<br />\n<br />\n1.當遇上很多事要處理時，他們往往會變得不知所措<br />\n<br />\n2.他們覺得吵鬧的環境一團混亂<br />\n高敏感族通常不適合在開放辦公室內工作，因為他們的感官會被聲音、氣味、視線還有人們來來去去所凌駕。<br />\n<br />\n3.肚子餓就生氣<br />\n<br />\n4.對他人的視線不自在<br />\n像是上台做簡報或是表演都會替他們帶來龐大的壓力，高敏感表現最好的時候就是他們處在私人時間的時候。<br />\n<br />\n5.深受藝術感動<br />\n<br />\n6.他們容易注意到他人的不舒服：<br />\nHSP 可以輕易察覺他人對環境的不適應，像是燈光需要調暗一點，或是音樂要關小聲一點，他們也很容易知道別人是否手足無措。<br />\n<br />\n7.當事情太多時他們會需要獨處充電<br />\n<br />\n8.避免暴力或恐怖媒體<br />\n<br />\n我覺得自己除咗3同8其他都中哂，特別係6，容易代入他人感受，但變咗容易受他人情緒影響。見到人地受苦難我個心會un住un住唔舒服好難受，就係所謂嘅同理心。<br />\n<br />\n好似每5個有1個，大家如果係高敏感族可以攞嚟做媾女話題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.suncolor.com.tw/event/books/highlysensitive/quiz.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.suncolor.com.tw%2Fevent%2Fbooks%2Fhighlysensitive%2Fquiz.html&d=TIKlq4bXcOIiQck3m%2BQSv1EyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=fe5829ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.suncolor.com.tw/event/books/highlysensitive/quiz.html</a>"},{"pid":"4a211a31efd158e5d633e6bef63de6848acc113b","tid":2381474,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T15:26:52.000Z","msg":"做到Q24<br />\n<br />\n發現48Q<br />\n<br />\n放棄了"},{"pid":"43f552e30e2b080d23f5f075b91fe514767337e3","tid":2381474,"uid":207476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T22:07:06.000Z","msg":"90分<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ec51102dbe27627e11b760efd2ac351c862b4ed","tid":2381474,"uid":30831,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T22:46:58.000Z","msg":"100分<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明白自己啲超能力了 但好廢 好容易做唔到野 成日都要用廢黎形容自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />覺得自己好易死 <br />\n飲唔黎有神經刺激嘅飲品 酒精 咖啡因<br />\n<br />\n有冇人都係聞到人哋感冒<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/awake.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"319b919738ca7060eefb84ad5d774d07ef689641","tid":2381474,"uid":290373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T22:59:41.000Z","msg":"121分<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea81d3101853b62fdd22d159a1e50b60bc3aa88c","tid":2381474,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T23:01:04.000Z","msg":"咪即係毒撚"},{"pid":"68bbb8abf270d3f1e66736d95495c54da26583cd","tid":2381474,"uid":213053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T18:27:12.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99d26368ee62c8a510c6f0d164973003eda41e2f","tid":2381474,"uid":291491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T18:28:13.000Z","msg":"基本上就係毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"942c39bc4e2a3d734b61af5a4182b4ea4fb03293","tid":2381474,"uid":249378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T18:32:13.000Z","msg":"93<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad36b040cf9e3aae252206e841c12ad43b739cd4","tid":2381474,"uid":32442,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T18:33:34.000Z","msg":"睇過本高敏感是種超能力<br />\n講咗啲優點 但係都無乜安慰感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47f8be9d52cb79c8e71e51a0cea5cc1670b8e03a","tid":2381474,"uid":92299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T18:40:10.000Z","msg":"屌 69<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"287ba042a75f4af5bfdbe4eab48d2396e0f5dfb5","tid":2381474,"uid":130466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T05:22:18.000Z","msg":"95<br />\n唔鍾意出街同人逼，食飯要自己一個唔鍾意嘈"}]}